{"tid":997382,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（無私奉獻）收養腦癱嬰23年　靚女護士為照顧對方單身至今","createTime":"2019-01-27T06:39:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-27T12:06:00.000Z","uid":22675,"like":16,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"67b73dcf5cebe8132253283cefda41085e0878eb","tid":997382,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T06:39:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20190127/photo/bkn-20190127012136577-0127_00952_001_04p.jpg?20190127020639\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20190127%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190127012136577-0127_00952_001_04p.jpg%3F20190127020639&h=4a122d5d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黑龍江牡丹江59歲女護士由艷麗，1996年在當地一個地盤中發現一名女嬰，於是將她帶走撫養23年。據悉當時有醫生表示，該名女嬰患有腦癱，更勸她將女嬰棄掉，否則會連累她一輩子。由女不忍如此，決定一手一腳將對方撫養成人，更為照顧女嬰，一直單身至今。 <br />\n<br />\n由女表示，當時該名醫生見到女嬰後，不單未施予援手，「人也不給我搶救你知道吧，你快去扔了得了，你得拖累你一輩子。」基於惻隱之心，由女決定將女嬰抱回家中照料，「從6個月到現在，23年，也沒斷了給她治療。」由女為了替養女治病，多年來奔波各地尋找良方。 <br />\n<br />\n由女的友人王凱表示，由艷麗「為了這孩子連家都沒成，我們有時候都說，我說你這是為了啥呀」。由女則解釋，自己最初也想為婚姻打算，「沒有合適的人，沒遇到緣分，後來一個階段就不想找了，這個經歷和愛是有限的，把所有的愛都給女兒了。」 <br />\n<br />\n由女表示，自己和養女有緣分，又稱自己收養對方「也跟我的職業有關，第一個感覺就是搶救，促使我的這種母愛吧。」她又稱，自己家住4樓，她的姊姊則住5樓，有時須靠姊姊夫妻兩人幫忙照顧養女，「沒有他們兩口子的支持，我由艷麗也不能堅持到今天。」"},{"pid":"815d90b784fdedbbcd2b66b9d2aea8b1c6de0068","tid":997382,"uid":40470,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T06:40:49.000Z","msg":"屌老主老母前我想公道d<br />\n<br />\n邊個係女嬰邊個係護士?"},{"pid":"7937ca13991e0dbc8b3c2c58a7a3e2a590974cef","tid":997382,"uid":22675,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T06:41:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20190127/photo/bkn-20190127012136577-0127_00952_001_02p.jpg?20190127020639\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20190127%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190127012136577-0127_00952_001_02p.jpg%3F20190127020639&h=fa2f7f0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n由女決定一手一腳將女嬰撫養成人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20190127/photo/bkn-20190127012136577-0127_00952_001_01p.jpg?20190127020639\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20190127%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190127012136577-0127_00952_001_01p.jpg%3F20190127020639&h=a231d625&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20190127/mobile/bkn-20190127012136577-0127_00952_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20190127%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190127012136577-0127_00952_001.html&d=%2BFEzSYEz1bTH5AdSBpjkdE%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=8d29fccd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20190127/mobile/bkn-20190127012136577-0127_00952_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"f68e14e99f1044e2144d04b317ad73d2c9566053","tid":997382,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T06:42:59.000Z","msg":"第一幅唔係女護士同腦癱嬰，貼錯sorry,第二幅先係"},{"pid":"567a0b4a8475fc3a1d281004047ebb0d17e5f58a","tid":997382,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T06:45:52.000Z","msg":"第一幅係路人甲王凱嚟"},{"pid":"02111c9146a0140d05ec31518126a285d62a809f","tid":997382,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T06:46:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9d5867dcbc271715ed5d0840594217a39e65885","tid":997382,"uid":42487,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T06:46:14.000Z","msg":"罕見大愛贏國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f8b513f7046c22cf1d3b07582c1f68a7c751b36","tid":997382,"uid":31208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T06:51:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 